name: Atlas Air 747-400 (WestJet Charter) Night Landing in Calgary ᴴᴰ
description:
Atlas Air Boeing 747-400 chartered by WestJet to clear up the backlog of passengers following inclement weather in Toronto.

This plane was configured in a high density configuration, seating over 450 passengers.
